<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.9.2">
<l>puṉaivaḷar pūmpoḻi lārpoṉṉi cūḻaraṅ kanakaruḷ</l>
<l>muṉaivaṉai mūvula kumpaṭait tamutal mūrttitaṉṉai</l>
<l>ciṉaivaḷar pūmpoḻil cūḻtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>kaṉaikaḻal kāṇuṅko lōkayal kaṇṇiyeṅ kārikaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will my kayal [fish]-eyed beauty see the rattling [war] anklets</l>
<l rend="indent">of the eminent one</l>
<l>In the city of Araṅkam surrounded by the full Poṉṉi [River]</l>
<l rend="indent">and verdant groves where laurel grows,</l>
<l>The primal form who created the three worlds, the one who stands</l>
<l>In Tirumāliruñcōlai encircled by verdant groves where bamboo grows?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
